h check requires JavaScript.'=>'Nangangailangan ng JavaScript ang Site Health check.','Site Health Info'=>'Impormasyon sa Kalusugan ng Site','This update does not work with your version of PHP.'=>'Hindi gumagana ang update na ito sa iyong bersyon ng PHP.','All formats'=>'Lahat ng format','Filter by post format'=>'I-filter ayon sa format ng post','Go to the Plugins screen'=>'Pumunta sa screen ng Plugins','The authenticity of %s could not be verified.'=>'Hindi na-verify ang pagiging tunay ng %s.','The authenticity of %s could not be verified as no signature was found.'=>'Hindi na-verify ang pagiging tunay ng %s dahil walang natagpuang lagda.','The authenticity of %s could not be verified as signature verification is unavailable on this system.'=>'Hindi na-verify ang pagiging tunay ng %s dahil hindi available ang pag-verify ng lagda sa system na ito.','Eraser callback is not valid: %s.'=>'Hindi balido ang eraser callback: %s.','Eraser does not include a callback: %s.'=>'Hindi kasama sa eraser ang isang callback: %s.','Sorry, you are not allowed to perform this action.'=>'Paumanhin, hindi ka pinapayagang gawin ang aksyon na ito.','HTTP requests have been blocked by the %1$s constant, with some allowed hosts: %2$s.'=>'Na-block ang mga HTTP request ng %1$s constant, na may ilang pinapayagang host: %2$s.','HTTP requests have been blocked by the %s constant, with no allowed hosts.'=>'Na-block ang mga HTTP request ng %s constant, na walang pinapayagang host.','Performance'=>'Performance','https://make.wordpress.org/hosting/handbook/handbook/server-environment/#php-extensions'=>'https://make.wordpress.org/hosting/handbook/handbook/server-environment/#php-extensions','You are using a %1$s drop-in which might mean that a %2$s database is not being used.'=>'Gumagamit ka ng %1$s na drop-in na maaaring nangangahulugang hindi ginagamit ang %2$s na database.','The WordPress Hosting Team maintains a list of those modules, both recommended and required, in <a href="%1$s" %2$s>the team